column2: SELECT    m.int_id, m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS dec1,     n.objid, n.distance,     o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2,    s.class, s.subclass, s.snMedian_g, s.class_person, s.zWarning, s.rChi2 into mydb.WD_fit from MyDB.table2 AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid     JOIN SpecObjAll s ON o.objID = s.bestObjID
